<typeStatus id="54C9880793508E0DF183FAE5FBE0FA5A" box="[958,1073,1399,1425]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">Lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693508E0DF666FAE5FEFDFA7E" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="diffinis" subGenus="Ophonus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793508E0DF666FAE5FA4DFA5A" box="[1115,1436,1399,1425]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">Harpalus (Ophonus) diffinis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF2AAFA09FEFDFA7E" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[151,300,1435,1461]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
design. by 
<collectorName id="2687537393508E0DF393FA0EFDF2FA7E" box="[430,547,1435,1462]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">J. Serrano</collectorName>
”
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E93508E0DF2FAFA2DFB23F946" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593508E0DF2FAFA2DFC18F9A1" blockId="9.[151,1437,1363,1678]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
The selected specimen hereby designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793508E0DF0FFFA2DFCF8FA12" box="[706,809,1471,1497]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">lectotype</typeStatus>
matches the data of the original description, and its diagnostic characters were highlighted by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF05EFA71FCD5FA36" author="Sciaky, R." box="[611,772,1507,1533]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" pagination="29 - 120" refId="ref12184" refString="Sciaky, R. (1987) Revisione delle specie paleartiche occidentali del genere Ophonus Dejean, 1821. Memoria della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 65, 29 - 120." type="journal article" year="1987">Sciaky (1987)</bibRefCitation>
, clearly showing the differences with its relative 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693508E0DF70AFA71FD8AF9EA" authority="(Lutshnik, 1922)" baseAuthorityName="Lutshnik" baseAuthorityYear="1922" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Ophonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ardosiacus" subGenus="Ophonus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793508E0DF70AFA71FE43F9EA" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">Ophonus (Ophonus) ardosiacus</emphasis>
(Lutshnik, 1922)
</taxonomicName>
. Other keys to identify the species are found in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF6BCF99AFAC5F9EA" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[1153,1300,1543,1570]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" pagination="344 - 386" refId="ref12516" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2004) Harpalina. In: Freude, H., Harde, K. W., Lohse, G. A. &amp; Klausnitzer, B. (Eds.), Die Kafer Mitteleuropas. Bd. 2 Adephaga 1: Carabidae (Laufkafer). Spektrum-Verlag, Heidelberg / Berlin, pp. 344 - 386." type="book chapter" year="2004">Wrase (2004</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF71CF995FA8CF9EA" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[1313,1373,1543,1569]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" refId="ref12634" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2011) Genus Tschitscherinellus. Arndt, E., Schnitter, P., Sfenthourakis, S. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (Eds.), Ground beetles (Carabidae) of Greece. Pensoft, Sofia, pp. 163." type="book" year="2011">2011</bibRefCitation>
). The species is currently included in the nominal subgenus, that is characterized by taxa of large body size and rounded posterior angles of pronotum, metallic dorsum, aedeagus with ligula, etc.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593508E0DF2FAF9E6FB23F946" blockId="9.[151,1437,1363,1678]" box="[199,1266,1651,1678]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
It is distributed in Central and Mediterranean Europe and the Levant (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF1E9F9E1FB37F946" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." box="[980,1254,1651,1678]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" pagination="1810" refId="ref11718" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (2017 c) Subtribe Harpalina Bonelli, 1810. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 1. Revised and Updated Edition. Brill, Leiden, pp. 515 - 562." type="book chapter" year="2017">Kataev &amp; Wrase, 2017c</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
